{"tid":515331,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇發覺廉航d 機師, 好多都叫captain cool ？","createTime":"2017-12-31T10:43:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T07:37:13.000Z","uid":123335,"like":46,"dislike":171,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"201576444f6acc3e9eabd9a559a36175c9ec18bb","tid":515331,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T10:43:44.000Z","msg":"我幾乎搭親廉航，都會聽到個機師自稱：captain cool .... 然後講一堆英文<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪d 廉航機師睇得太多TVB<br />\n煲得太多衝上雲霄，high大左以為自己係cool 魔，個個都爭住叫captain cool <br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪d 廉航機師先會玩呢d 低級趣味<br />\n有冇巴打搭開國泰, BA 果d ? <br />\n想問人地大公司d 機師係咪會成熟d 唔會自稱captain cool ？<br />\n<br />\n邊間廉航就唔開名啦<br />\n廢事影響人地聲譽做生意<br />\n佢地可能見返工悶先扮cool 魔自high 下姐<br />\n我都唔想影響佢揾食既<br />\n<br />\n不過個個都FF自己係cool 魔<br />\n真係笑撚死"},{"pid":"417f180f941574c3b526ad31bbd9ce301d167de7","tid":515331,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"J凳"},{"pid":"ebb6cf044aa0b4fc6546ff038574d814e5586f04","tid":515331,"uid":143953,"like":226,"dislike":26,"score":200,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T10:48:21.000Z","msg":"Captain crew"},{"pid":"52fa9e3b8977a8260fbe95fb1975f14a41d71d0e","tid":515331,"uid":70679,"like":148,"dislike":5,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"cabin crew"},{"pid":"c963f0a62cefd6c87f1d1b76b81d876d7d10964e","tid":515331,"uid":77453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T10:49:26.000Z","msg":"Cabin cool<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a33d89cab4c456ca5bc5509a34523bd3ce7e990","tid":515331,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"cabin crew"},{"pid":"f9592570d36e03f77244d6fb17be3d6748abeed2","tid":515331,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"803a77cc407e8dbd0d95c7c58b699989e3e223eb","tid":515331,"uid":7079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB